snippet.title: Diana Helps Santa delivering Christmas presents
snippet.description:
Christmas is coming soon and everyone is waiting for their presents. But Santa Claus is sleeping. Diana decides to help Santa Claus deliver presents. A wonderful Christmas story for children.
